# Testing

Write tests with the implementation, not after.

## Setup

- Vitest; `"test": "vitest run"` in each app/lib `package.json`
- Colocate as `*.test.ts` (e.g. `logic/score.ts` → `logic/score.test.ts`)

## What to test

- `logic/`: required — happy path + boundary/empty (≥1 each)
- `lib/` public API: required — cover all exports
- `ui/`: optional; prefer logic extraction. Complex UI state → `@testing-library` only if needed

## Done when

1. `npm test` passes
2. `npm run build` succeeds → `docs/<app-name>/`
3. No “should work” without tests; never commit with failing tests
